@startuml credential_session_start_sequence
' cc-tunnel がセッション開始時に credentials を取り出して使うフロー

title Credential Session Start Sequence (cc-tunnel)

actor "User" as user
participant "Frontend\n(ChatView)" as fe
participant "cc-tunnel API\nHandler" as handler
participant "CredentialService" as credsvc
database "PostgreSQL\ncredentials" as db
participant "ExecutionProvider\n(Local/DockerGCE)" as provider
participant "SessionManager" as sm
participant "Session Container\n(cc-remote-agent)" as container

note over user, container
  前提:
  - User は app-auth でログイン済み
  - credentials は cc-login 経由で DB に登録済み（または未登録）
end note

== Case 1: credentials が登録済み・有効 ==

user -> fe : メッセージ送信
fe -> handler : POST /conversations/{id}/messages\n(Bearer token)

handler -> handler : token → username 解決
handler -> credsvc : FetchAndDecrypt(ctx, username)
credsvc -> db : SELECT encrypted_data, nonce, key_version, is_valid\nWHERE username=$1
db --> credsvc : row (is_valid=TRUE)
credsvc -> credsvc : key_version 確認 → 該当鍵で\n  AES-GCM Open(key, nonce, ciphertext, AAD=username)
credsvc --> handler : credentials_json (平文)

handler -> provider : Execute(ctx, req, onEvent, credentials_json)
provider -> sm : GetOrCreate(conversationID, credentials_json)

alt 新規セッション
  sm -> sm : tmpfs:/home/user/.claude を持つ container spec を構築
  sm -> container : ContainerCreate + Start
  sm -> container : POST /init\n{credentialsJson: "..."}\n(cc-remote-agent が /home/user/.claude/.credentials.json に書き込む)
  container --> sm : 200 {ready: true}
end

sm -> container : POST /execute (会話実行)
container -> container : claude CLI 起動 → API 呼び出し
container --> sm : NDJSON stream (events)
sm --> provider : events
provider --> handler : onEvent
handler --> fe : 202 Accepted (背景で処理継続)

== Case 2: credentials 未登録 ==

user -> fe : メッセージ送信
fe -> handler : POST /conversations/{id}/messages

handler -> credsvc : FetchAndDecrypt(ctx, username)
credsvc -> db : SELECT ... WHERE username=$1
db --> credsvc : (no rows)
credsvc --> handler : ErrCredentialsNotFound

handler --> fe : 401 {\n  error: "credentials_required",\n  redirect: "/login/credentials?reason=missing"\n}

fe -> user : 「認証情報が必要です」表示\n→ /login/credentials へ自動遷移

== Case 3: credentials が無効化されている ==

user -> fe : メッセージ送信
fe -> handler : POST /conversations/{id}/messages

handler -> credsvc : FetchAndDecrypt(ctx, username)
credsvc -> db : SELECT ... WHERE username=$1
db --> credsvc : row (is_valid=FALSE)
credsvc --> handler : ErrCredentialsInvalid

handler --> fe : 401 {\n  error: "credentials_invalid",\n  redirect: "/login/credentials?reason=expired"\n}

fe -> user : 「再ログインが必要です」表示

== Case 4: メッセージ送信中に Anthropic API が 401 ==

note over container
  実行中、claude CLI が
  401 Unauthorized を返した場合
end note

container --> sm : event {type: "error", code: 401}
sm --> provider : エラー伝播
provider -> credsvc : MarkInvalid(ctx, username)
credsvc -> db : UPDATE credentials\nSET is_valid=FALSE\nWHERE username=$1
db --> credsvc : OK

provider --> handler : 完了イベント (failed)
handler --> fe : SSE/poll で "failed" 通知

note right of fe
  次回送信時には Case 3 のフローで
  401 redirect が返り、再ログインへ
end note

@enduml
